flowchart LR
    subgraph Failures
        F1[Worker crash]
        F2[Lock TTL expires]
        F3[DB unavailable]
        F4[Duplicate claim]
    end

    subgraph Detection
        D1[Heartbeat stops]
        D2[locked_until past now]
        D3[Health check fails]
        D4[SKIP LOCKED]
    end

    subgraph Recovery
        R1[Stale detector releases jobs]
        R2[Job re-claimable]
        R3[API degraded / workers retry]
        R4[Prevented at DB level]
    end

    F1 --> D1 --> R1
    F2 --> D2 --> R2
    F3 --> D3 --> R3
    F4 --> D4 --> R4
